::Shadow Wing::

She hit and punched around everywhere she could make contact.  It 
wasrather a tight fit in the tiger's mouth. 
"Get me out of here! Blast you you pred! Put me down now!"  she tried 
to reach her knife, but she couldn't. She turned and a tooth was 
right at her ribcage.  If the tiger bit down, she was a goner.
